;断桥花妖，见到人就扑上来砍，血少于50%时治疗(582)自己,一定几率使用就擒(572),血少逃跑
[common]
0:if(AIS_GetHP()<50&AIS_IsCanSkill(582)=1){AIS_ToSkill(582);AIS_SetTimes(1);AIS_SetPRI(34);};血少于50%时治疗(582)自己
1:if(AIS_GetAIState()=SATTACK&AIS_GetHP()<20){AIS_ToFlee(1);AIS_SetTimes(1);AIS_SetPRI(36);};生命少于20%的时候向距离最近的队友逃跑
2:if(AIS_GetAIState()=SATTACK&AIS_Rand()<10&AIS_IsCanSkill(572)=1){AIS_ToSkill(572);AIS_SetTimes(1);AIS_SetPRI(33);};在攻击状态10%的机率释放572号技能，次数1
[commonend]

